The Proposal: -
Regarding various queries of contractual employees working under Samagra Shiksha Yojana, Shri. The Chief Minister's

Under the chairmanship of The meeting was held at Sayadri Guest House on 22.7.2024. During the meeting, Shri. The Chief Minister made recommendations to the government regarding various issues of these employees.
A committee has been constituted to look into the matter. Accordingly, the committee was constituted. 04.03.2025

According to the government's decision. The committee was reconstituted by overturning the government decision of 14.10.2024. The committee is working under the Samagra Shiksha Scheme after reviewing it for administrative reasons.
Formation of a revised Committee to make recommendations to the Government on various issues of contractual employees.
It was under the consideration of the government.
The Government's Decisions:

The reference d. The Committee constituted under this Government Decision to make recommendations with regard to the issue of contractual employees under the Samagra Shiksha Scheme under the Government Decision dated 04.03.2025.
is being overridden.
The Committee is being reconstituted as follows to make recommendations to the Government on various issues of contractual employees working under the Samagra Shiksha Scheme.
